# STREAMING::GET_PLAYER_SWITCH_INTERP_OUT_DURATION

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
returns the duration of any interpolation out of an establishing shot, in milliseconds, or 0 if invalid
